- **Architecture Decision Records** (init, create, list, link ADRs in `docs/adr`; requires `adr-tools`): use the [manage-adr](.claude/skills/manage-adr/SKILL.md) skill.
- **Changelog** (init, add fragments, batch releases, merge into CHANGELOG; requires `changie`): use the [manage-changelog](.claude/skills/manage-changelog/SKILL.md) skill.
